### Get All Users
GET https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Favorite Teams of a User
GET https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users/favorites/teams
Accept: application/json

### Add a Favorite Team
POST https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users/favorites/teams/New York Yankees
Accept: application/json

### Add a Favorite Team
POST https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users/favorites/teams/Los Angeles Dodgers
Accept: application/json

### Add a Favorite Team
POST https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users/favorites/teams/Team1
