### Edit all fields of the user's profile
PATCH https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "televisor"
}

### Edit only one field of the user's profile
PATCH https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com"
}

### Edit profile with invalid email pattern
PATCH https://localhost:8443/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bad_email",
  "password": "televisor"
}


